fields.name: Television
fields.description: LG TVs offer stunning picture quality and smart features. Experience vibrant colors, deep blacks, and crisp details on a range of screen sizes, from sleek OLEDs to affordable LED models. Enjoy your favorite shows, movies, and games with advanced technology like AI ThinQ and webOS.

fields.name: Power Bank
fields.description: A power bank is a portable charger that provides power to electronic devices like smartphones and tablets. It's a convenient solution for charging on the go, especially when there's no access to a wall outlet.

fields.name: Airpods 3
fields.description: The AirPods (3rd generation) deliver immersive sound with Spatial Audio and Adaptive EQ. Their comfortable design and long battery life make them perfect for listening to music, taking calls, and enjoying your favorite content on the go.

fields.name: Logitech Mouse
fields.description: Logitech wireless mice offer comfort, precision, and convenience. With a range of options, from basic to advanced, you can find the perfect mouse to suit your needs. Enjoy wireless freedom, ergonomic design, and reliable connectivity for seamless computing.
